oeneck is also home to the Schoeneck Volunteer Fire Company. [[File:Schoeneck1-9-1.jpg|thumb|left|alt=Schoeneck Engine 1-9-1.|Engine 1-9-1 ''Schoeneck, Pennsylvania''.]] [[File:Schoeneck1-9-2.jpg|thumb|center|alt=Schoeneck Engine 1-9-1.|Engine 1-9-2 ''Schoeneck, Pennsylvania''.]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070817005606/http://www.cocalico.k12.pa.us/elem/schoe/index.html Schoeneck Elementary School]\n\n{{Lancaster County, Pennsylvania}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Lancaster County, Pennsylvania]]\n", "text_old": "{{More citations needed|date=November 2007}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                     = Schoeneck, Pennsylvania\n|official_name            = \n|settlement_type          = [[Census-designated place]]\n|nickname                 = \n|motto                    =\n\n<!-- Images -->\n|image_skyline            = \n|imagesize                = \n|image_caption            = \n|image_flag               = \n|image_seal               =\n\n<!-- Maps -->\n|pushpin_map              = USA Pennsylvania\n|pushpin_label_position   = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_map_caption      = Location within the U.S. state of Pennsylvania\n|pushpin_mapsize          = \n|image_map                = \n|map_caption              = Location within Lancaster county\n\n<!-- Location -->\n|subdivision_type         = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name         = United States\n|subdivision_type1        = [[U.S. state|State]]\n|subdivision_name1        = [[Pennsylvania]]\n|subdivision_type2        = [[List of counties in Pennsylvania|County]]\n|subdivision_name2        = [[Lancaster County, Pennsylvania|Lancaster]]\n\n|subdivision_type3        = Township\n|subdivision_name3        = [[West Cocalico Township, Pennsylvania|West Cocalico]]\n|government_footnotes     = \n|government_type          = \n|leader_title             = <!-- 