eshardware.com/Spades/read.php?article_id=5000175 Recipe For Revival: K6-2+] at AcesHardware.Com (archived)\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20050524225737/http://www.aceshardware.com/Spades/read.php?article_id=25000222 K6-III+: Super-7 to the Limit] at AcesHardware.Com (archived)\n\n{{AMD processors}}\n\n[[Category:Advanced Micro Devices x86 microprocessors|K06-3]]\n[[Category:Superscalar microprocessors]]\n", "name_user": "Analitikos", "label": "safe", "comment": "end of production", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AMD_K6-III"}
